E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to Logan #2: When Calvin and Dave's college basketball teams face off, Dave surprises the Butlers with tickets and also invites one of his friends. (S1 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Camping Trip: When the Johnsons invite the Butlers to go camping, Dave is taken aback by Calvin's idea of roughing it. (S1 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Repass: The Butlers host a memorial when a curmudgeonly neighbour passes away. And Calvin learns something unexpected about himself. (S1 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Conversation: Dave's thrilled when Calvin invites him golfing. But does Calvin have an ulterior motive? (S1 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Five Minutes: Mitch and Cam have five minutes to catch a flight, and Haley and Rainer are forced to re-evaluate their entire relationship in five minutes. (S8 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Frank's Wedding: Frank Dunphy's Roaring Twenties-themed wedding day is finally here, and to get into the spirit, Phil gets the Dunphy clan to show up in costume. (S8 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Zocalo: Gordon Ramsay visits a floundering Mexican restaurant which has become an albatross around the necks of its owners, married couple Greg and Mary Russell. (S5 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Spin a Yarn: Gordon tries to save the struggling Spin a Yarn restaurant in California. Despite an expensive refurbishment, the business is tearing apart its owners' marriage. (S5 Ep13) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Behind the Laughter: A behind-the-scenes look at the Simpson family. How did they win their fame? And how did they cope when the showbiz pressure got too much? (S11 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Springfield Splendor: Lisa and Marge team up on a graphic novel that becomes a musical. But Marge takes all the credit... (S29 Ep2/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Locomotion Interruption: Leonard and Amy take an impromptu road trip to Arizona to pick up Sheldon when his epic railway journey ends in chaos. Penny has an interview. (S8 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Junior Professor Solution: When Sheldon has to teach a course at the university, Howard enrols in his class. Tension brews between Penny and Bernadette. (S8 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Disneyland: Nothing is more quintessential to good old family fun than a trip to Disneyland - but not without a side of motion sickness, achy feet and a wayward toddler. (S3 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Tableau Vivant: Jay and Gloria get on each other's nerves while trying to order lunch, and Cam and Claire can't agree on how to discipline children. (S3 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Collaboration Fluctuation: Leonard, Penny and Raj settle into their new living arrangement, and Sheldon expresses an interest in Amy's professional life. (S10 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Recollection Dissipation: Sheldon collaborates on two projects - one with Leonard and Howard, plus another with Amy - pushing himself to the limit. (S10 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Separation Agitation: Howard and Bernadette are upset when they leave Halley at the nursery. Bert the geologist introduces his girlfriend to the gang. (S10 Ep21/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cognition Regeneration: Leonard isn't happy when he finds out that Penny is considering accepting a job offer from her ex-boyfriend Zack. (S10 Ep22/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Suicide Squad: Desperate circumstances call for desperate measures as Peralta, Captain Holt and the team are forced to ally themselves with some old enemies. (S6 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Manhunter: Jake leads a manhunt after an assassination attempt is made on a city councillor. Holt adjusts to his new position as a uniformed officer. (S7 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Left Behind: Flanders loses his job and comes to work with Homer at the power plant. Homer prays for him to be fired. (S29 Ep19/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Throw Grampa from the Dane: The Simpsons visit Denmark and all fall in love with it - except Homer. Meanwhile, Grampa needs a serious operation. (S29 Ep20/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Novelization Correlation: Amy appears on the Professor Proton show. Penny hates the idea that the female protagonist in Leonard's novel is based on her. (S11 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Neonatal Nomenclature: Bernadette's friends try various tactics to help her go into labour. (S11 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Athenaeum Allocation: Leonard jumps through hoops to secure the perfect wedding venue for Sheldon and Amy. Howard and Bernadette face a big decision. (S11 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Gates Excitation: The guys do everything in their power to meet Bill Gates when his firm has dealings with the pharmaceutical company Penny works for. (S11 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: G.I. (Annoyed Grunt): Homer accidentally signs up for basic training in the army. And Marge and Grampa get roped in when they try to get him released. (S18 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Moe 'n' a Lisa: Lisa discovers Moe's poetic talent and helps get him published. And he's so successful that he - and the Simpsons - are invited to a literary conference. (S18 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Four Great Women and a Manicure: On a visit to the nail salon, Marge and Lisa discuss whether a woman can be simultaneously clever, powerful and beautiful. (S20 Ep20/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Man Who Came to Be Dinner: A new amusement park ride transports the Simpsons to Kang and Kodos's home planet, where they're held captive in a zoo. (S26 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Supercruising: Life at Sea
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the North Africa and Europe voyage, the chefs prepare a fine-dining experience with a difference, while the Caribbean cruisers enjoy tranquil bamboo rafting in the scorching heat. (Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Oblivion
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2013) Sci-fi action-mystery set on a war-ravaged planet Earth that's been largely abandoned by humanity. With Tom Cruise, Andrea Riseborough, Olga Kurylenko and Morgan Freeman.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction's Best Naughty...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Bits: We celebrate the pickers whose initial naked attraction led to full-on romance, as well as those whose dates were disasters.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction: All Out & Proud
E4Plus1.uk.description: This Pride special rides the rainbow and celebrates memorable singletons from across the sexual spectrum who've sashayed into the pods.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the box in this episode, After Life, This Morning, Coronation Street, Britain's Got Talent, Jamie: Keep Cooking and Carry On, and BBC News on Trump vs China. (S15 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Below Deck Sailing Yacht
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mid-Strife Crisis: The boat is doused in glam as a drag queen duo come aboard. But will it be a show-stopping stay or will the team tank on the big stage? (S5 Ep13/16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mook, the Chef, the Wife and Her Homer: Homer becomes the boss of Fat Tony's mob when Tony's son decides to become a chef rather than go into the family business. (S18 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Four Great Women and a Manicure: On a visit to the nail salon, Marge and Lisa discuss whether a woman can be simultaneously clever, powerful and beautiful. (S20 Ep20/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ten Years Later: Claire is determined to make up for her less-than-joyful mood at Jay and Gloria's wedding by throwing their 10th-anniversary party. (S9 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Winner Winner Turkey Dinner: During Jay's Thanksgiving toast, he honours the entire family on their recent successes, even though everyone knows that they aren't quite true. (S9 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Re-Rack: Dave is eager to take on a bigger role in the community and prove himself to Calvin. (S2 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Bully: When Grover gets into a fight at school, Gemma is torn between her job and her desire to protect her son. (S2 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goldbergs' Excellent Adventure: The family look for a way to honour Pops' memory. (S9 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Horse Play: As Beverly disrupts Adam's college admission plans, Erica discovers that her future father-in-law blames her for a prank she didn't pull. (S9 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Riptide Waters: Barry and Adam join forces to save a water park that's being threatened with closure. Wedding planning opens a rift between Beverly and Erica. (S9 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The William Penn Years: Adam makes an inspirational video about a football game against William Penn's rival. Beverly and Murray try to buy a neighbour's house. (S9 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: An Itch Like No Other: Barry's poison ivy causes problems for Erica and Geoff. And having Mr Glascott living next door presents a challenge for the whole family. (S9 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Wedding March 5: My Boyfriend's Back: (2019) Romance
E4Plus1.uk.description: There's a new wedding planner at Willow Lake. Thing is, her ex is the best man at the wedding she's planning. Awks. Can Olivia resist helping her young protégé out?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Made in Chelsea
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Alice and Sam Vanderpump nervously plan to tell Sam's aunt - the formidable Lisa Vanderpump - about their pregnancy. Jazz uncovers a shocking secret. (S30 Ep6/10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Greek at the Harbor: Gordon Ramsay helps a family-run Greek restaurant turn its fortunes around in Ventura Harbor in California. But he uncovers a shocking family secret... (S5 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: El Greco: Gordon Ramsay visits struggling Greek restaurant El Greco, where the owners have secretly recruited 'Chef Mike' the microwave to help them out on a daily basis. (S5 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hotel Transylvania 3
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2018) Spooky animated family comedy. On a monster-friendly cruise, Dracula (Adam Sandler) falls in love - with a vampire slayer!

E4Plus1.uk.title: Lemony Snicket's A Series of...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Unfortunate Events: (2004) Gothic family comedy starring Jim Carrey as the evil, scheming Count Olaf, who'll do whatever it takes to deprive three young orphans of their inheritance.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The First Pitch Insufficiency: Howard's nervous when NASA ask him to throw the first pitch at a baseball game. Sheldon claims his and Amy's relationship is the best in the gang. (S8 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hook-Up Reverberation: Raj's honesty about his past comes back to haunt him when his girlfriend Emily gives Penny the cold shoulder. The guys consider an investment. (S8 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Focus Attenuation: The guys attempt to invent something of scientific importance but only come up with new and enjoyable ways to procrastinate. (S8 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Expedition Approximation: Sheldon and Raj try to find out if they could survive a dark-matter research expedition in a salt mine by simulating the conditions in a tunnel. (S8 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jazzy and the Pussycats: Bart takes up playing the drums, upstages Lisa and joins a top jazz band. So Lisa turns her back on music and starts rescuing animals instead. (S18 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Please Homer Don't Hammer 'Em: Marge discovers that she has a gift for carpentry, but has to use Homer as a cover in order to overcome prejudices against women builders. (S18 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror XVII: Homer ingests a blob from an asteroid; Bart enslaves a clay monster; and everyone thinks that aliens are invading. (S18 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: G.I. (Annoyed Grunt): Homer accidentally signs up for basic training in the army. And Marge and Grampa get roped in when they try to get him released. (S18 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: This time, many of Britain's best-loved personalities watch The Baby, One Question, Million Pound Pawn, CODA, America the Beautiful, The Laundry Guy, and The One That Got Away. (S4 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch Trigger Point, One Day, Married at First Sight Australia, Sort Your Life Out, Into the Congo with Ben Fogle, Earthsounds and This Morning. (S23 Ep4)
